<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN274-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai - atu; tuṟai - erumaimaṟam. ulōccaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Pn274">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>nīlak kaccaip pūvā rāṭaip</l>
<l>pīlik kaṇṇip peruntakai maṟavaṉ</l>
<l>mēlvaruṅ kaḷiṟṟoṭu vēṟuran tiṉiyē</l>
<l>taṉṉun tuṟakkuvaṉ pōlu moṉṉala</l>
<l>reḵkuṭai valattar māvoṭu parattarak</l>
<l>kaiyiṉ vāṅkit taḻīi</l>
<l>moympi ṉūkki meykkoṇ ṭaṉaṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The bold man, a paragon with a blue belt,</l>
<l>a garment full of flowers [and] a peacock feather chaplet,</l>
<l>after driving [his] spear against the elephant bull coming up against [him],</l>
<l>now is giving himself up, it seems. While the enemies</l>
<l>spread, strong men with blades along with horses,</l>
<l>he dragged/bent [them] with [his] hands [and] embraced [them] </l>
<l>swinging [them] with force he took [them] onto [his] body.</l> 
</lg>
    </div>
